title: Rocket League Micro RC Car - Dominus
features: The Rocket League Micro RC Car Dominus is a full-function remote control replica vehicle, modeled with realistic game-inspired features such as lights and quick acceleration.
This 2.75”/ 69mm ride is a 2.4Ghz micro Remote Control Car that features working headlights and taillights, and includes a goal, game ball, and controller.
These Rocket League Micro RC Cars come with special downloadable content (DLC) that unlocks unique gameplay on the video game and twitch.
The game ball controller also charges and stores the vehicle, so you can easily get driving wherever you go!
Take your favorite Rocket League vehicle out of the screen and into your hands! Appropriate for ages 5 and up.
